snippet.title: ZX81 Jetpac Game play
snippet.description: Jetpac for the Sinclair ZX81. Written entirely in machine code this game has four types of alien and two spaceships to build. This is not a direct copy of the Spectrum game but follows the same game play. Unlike the original, it features redefinable keys and selectable difficulty levels. Download this game as an emulator file or as an MP3 for loading onto an original machine from http://bukstergames.bizhat.com/
